Your task is to develop a Task Planner web app

Main audience - folks from big IT company

Core features:
- Task items should have Name (100 symbols), Description (1k symbols), Due Date (Date time)
- It should be possible to add or remove tasks
- It should be possible to mark tasks as completed

Technologies
- Web based app
- it should support desktop web interface, but not necessarily tablets and phones
- .NET Core + Razor Pages
- Very simple authentication, just user name, not password
- Use a persistent file-based storage
- No integrations
- Use MS Project-like design/UI
- No compliance requirements
- Add localization: EN and UA languages
- Deploy this app on a localhost
- No logs or analytics needed, besides proper error handling
